                 DARK AGES:  VOLUME ONE -- "PRINCE OF DESTINY"

                             >>> Version 1.00 <<<

                                 Published by
                         Apogee Software Productions
 
                         Developed and Programmed by 
                              Scenario Software

      Dark Ages is a brilliant arcade/adventure game with superb graphics
        and animation.  It is also the first shareware game to support
          both Ad Lib and Sound Blaster, the two leading sound cards.

     The graphics in Dark Ages are so demanding that the game will not run
      fast enough on old, slow 8088 and 8086 based PCs.  You will need an
      80286, an 80386 or a faster processor to play Dark Ages at its best.

      It is also recommended that you play Dark Ages with as few TSRs as
        possible running, else you might experience keyboard problems.

  Apogee Software has many other exciting games, please send $6 if you would
   like a sample disk of other great games.  Mention disk size and the type
               of graphics system (CGA, EGA or VGA) that you have.

       Everyone who orders Dark Ages will be notified when future games
                are released--and many, many more are coming!

                    Thanks, and have fun with Dark Ages!

